<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Blogginit</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container my-5">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white">
                <h2>Welcome to Blogginit!</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <p>Hi {{ user.name }},</p>
                <p>Thank you for joining Blogginit! We're excited to have you on board.</p>
                <p>Your verification code is:</p>
                <h3 class="text-center text-success">{{ verification_code }}</h3>
                <p>Please use this code to verify your account and get started.</p>
                <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to our support team.</p>
                <p>Happy blogging!</p>
                <p>Best regards,</p>
                <p><strong>The Blogginit Team</strong></p>
            </div>
            <div class="card-footer text-muted text-center">
                &copy; {{ "now"|date("Y") }} Blogginit. All rights reserved.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>